flowchart TD
    Start([POST /api/novo/vitals/record]) --> Auth{Está Autenticado?}
    Auth -- Não --> Error401[401 Unauthorized]
    Auth -- Sim --> Validation{Zod: Dados Válidos?}
    
    Validation -- Não --> Error400[400 Bad Request]
    Validation -- Sim --> CalcSeverity[Calcular Severidade - MEWS Logic]
    
    subgraph MEWS [Lógica de Severidade]
    direction TB
    CalcSeverity --> SYST[Pressão Sistólica]
    CalcSeverity --> TEMP[Temperatura]
    CalcSeverity --> HR[Frequência Cardíaca]
    CalcSeverity --> O2[Saturação O2]
    end
    
    MEWS --> GetOverallSeverity{Severidade Final}
    GetOverallSeverity --> |CRITICAL| SeverCR[Status: CRITICAL]
    GetOverallSeverity --> |ALERT/WARNING| SeverAL[Status: ALERT]
    GetOverallSeverity --> |NORMAL| SeverNO[Status: NORMAL]

    SeverCR & SeverAL & SeverNO --> StreakLogic[Calcular Streak]
    
    subgraph Streak [Lógica de Ofensiva]
    direction TB
    StreakLogic --> CheckLast[Check lastActiveAt]
    CheckLast --> |Ativo Ontem| Incr[Streak + 1]
    CheckLast --> |Pulou Dia| Reset[Streak = 1]
    CheckLast --> |Já Ativo Hoje| Keep[Mantém Streak]
    end

    Incr & Reset & Keep --> Save[Prisma Transaction: Save VitalRecord + Update User]
    Save --> Success([201 Created + New Streak])

    style MEWS fill:#f0f7ff,stroke:#005fb8,stroke-width:2px
    style Streak fill:#fff7e6,stroke:#d46b08,stroke-width:2px
    style Success fill:#f6ffed,stroke:#52c41a,stroke-width:2px
